# (Oops, there goes
a billion-kilowatt dam)

01:16:01.840 --> 01:16:05.276
# So keep your high hopes

01:16:05.360 --> 01:16:08.158
# Keep your high hopes

01:16:08.240 --> 01:16:13.917
# Keep those high apple pie
in the sky hopes

